28:1 COMMENT "# Generic type dissection: a match on a generic type parameter selects"
28:71 EOL "\n"
29:1 COMMENT "# code paths at compile time -- during monomorphisation the concrete"
29:69 EOL "\n"
30:1 COMMENT "# type is known and only the matching arm survives. See doc/spec.html."
30:71 EOL "\n"
